  <brief_title>Combination Chemotherapy Plus Radiation Therapy in Treating Patients With Anaplastic Astrocytoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Trial of Pre-Irradiation Chemotherapy With BCNU, Cisplatin and Oral Etoposide Combined With Radiation Therapy in the Treatment of Grade 3 Astrocytoma (Anaplastic Astrocytoma)</official_title>
